3) MUC 5.3: "SIMULATING A SINGLE STEP"
- Muc tieu:
  + Mo phong chinh xac 1 buoc chuyen tiep cua QTM M tren cau hinh da ma hoa.

3.1) Bieu dien dia phuong 3 o bang
- r = p s1 sigma1 s2 sigma2 s3 sigma3:
  + p: trang thai noi.
  + sigma_i: ky hieu bang o 3 o lien tiep.
  + s_i in {2,3}: marker vi tri dau doc (2 = dang quet o i, 3 = khong quet).
- Target:
  + r la target neu (s1,s2,s3)=(3,2,3) va delta(p,sigma2) duoc dinh nghia.
- Pre-target:
  + Bo p di, chi giu s1 sigma1 s2 sigma2 s3 sigma3.

3.2) Flag qubit va ham f8
- Them 1 qubit co |0> lam co bao:
  + |0>: chua mo phong buoc nay.
  + |1>: da mo phong buoc nay.
- f8 co y tuong:
  + Neu khoi hien tai la target: ap dung transition delta va bat flag thanh |1>.
  + Neu khong: giu nguyen.
- g_r va h_r:
  + h_r nhan biet mau target |tilde(r)>.
  + g_r thuc thi bien doi noi dung 3 o + trang thai noi theo delta.
- Vi sao hop le:
  + Do M well-formed nen cac anh xa tren cac target tao he truc chuan, giu duoc norm.
- Ket hop:
  + g = Compo[{g_r'}_{r in T}], voi g_r' = Branch[g_r o h_r, I].
  + f8 = REMOVE_1 o (g^{<=ell+13} otimes I).

3.3) Ham F2 quet toan bo bang
- Van de:
  + f8 xu ly 1 khoi cuc bo, can ap dung tren moi cua so 3-o.
- Cach lam:
  + Dung REP_{ell+1} de dua (flag, q) len dau khoi can xu ly.
  + Ap dung f8 co dieu kien do dai.
  + Dung REMOVE_{ell+1} dua ve vi tri cu.
- F2':
  + De quy theo khoi 4 bit de duyet het bang.
- F2 = REP_{ell+1} o F2' o REMOVE_{ell+1}.
- Ket qua:
  + Sau 1 lan F2, flag doi |0> -> |1>, danh dau da mo phong xong 1 step.

4) MUC 5.4: HOAN TAT MO PHONG TOAN BO
- Muc tieu:
  + Lap lai mo phong 1 step dung p(|x|) lan.
- Y tuong:
  + Moi vong: ap NOT o F2 de reset flag tu |1> ve |0> de dung lai duoc.
  + Lap chinh xac p(|x|) lan bang de quy 1-qubit.
- Ham:
  + g_hat = Skip[NOT o F2]
  + F3 = QRec_1[I, Branch[g_hat, I], I | F3, I]
- Y nghia:
  + F3 dong vai tro "engine" mo phong day du computation cua QTM tren vung ma hoa.

5) MUC 5.5: CHUAN BI OUTPUT
- Muc tieu phan 1 Bo de 4.3:
  + Dua ma output tilde(M[r]) len dau trai qustring.
- Muc tieu phan 2 Bo de 4.3:
