5.1) Cac buoc i-iv (va tong hop F4)
- f9: doi marker cuoi hat(3) -> hat(1) de danh dau duoi.
- f10: day dan cac cap hat(3)hat(b) ben trai xuong cuoi bang REMOVE_4 co de quy.
- h8: boc tach marker hat(1),hat(2),hat(3) ra cuoi, giu lai chuoi du lieu ma output.
- h9: doi ky hieu cuoi hat(b) <-> hat(2) de tao dung ket thuc ma.
- F4 = h9 o h8 o f10 o f9.
- Ket qua:
  + Trang thai co dang sum_r |tilde(M[r])>|xi_hat_{x,r}>.
  + Bao toan noi tich/chuan va truc giao can thiet theo dieu kien Bo de 4.3.

5.2) Lay output khong ma hoa
- Dung g7 (de quy + REMOVE_1) de giai ma phan dau.
- Dat F5 = g7 o F4.
- Thu duoc dang |M[r]> o phan output can doc.
- Day la buoc chot de hoan tat chung minh Bo de 4.3.

6) MUC 5.6: UNG DUNG PHU CUA THU TUC MO PHONG
- Tu cac buoc trong 5.2, tac gia rut ra 2 cong cu doc lap:
  + Encode/Decode (Bo de 5.1)
  + COPY_2 (Bo de 5.2)

6.1) Bo de 5.1 - Encode/Decode
- Encode:
  + Encode(|0^{k+1}1> otimes |phi>) = sum_{s in {0,1}^k} (|tilde(s)> otimes |s><s|phi>)
  + Tuc ma hoa k bit dau cua |phi> thanh dang tilde(s), tieu thu bo dem 0^k1.
- Decode:
  + La nghich dao cua Encode.
  + Thuoc mu square_1^QP nhờ tinh dong duoi nghich dao (Menh de 3.5).

6.2) Bo de 5.2 - COPY_2
- Noi dung:
  + Co the sao chep thong tin co dien da ma hoa, khong vi pham no-cloning vi doi tuong la chuoi co dien.
- Cong thuc:
  + COPY_2(|tilde(0^k)> otimes |phi>)
    = sum_s (|tilde(s)> otimes |tilde(s)><tilde(s)|phi>)
- Y nghia ky thuat:
  + Dung de duplicate nhan/du lieu co dien trong cac buoc uncompute va rut trich output.

7) MUC 6 - HUONG NGHIEN CUU TUONG LAI

7.1) Muc 6.1 - Schematic definition hop ly hon
- Van de:
  + square_1^QP hien tai du de dac trung FBQP, nhung co the chua "dep"/"toi uu".
- Vi du QFT:
  + Dang tong quat tren so qubit tuy y co the khong bieu dien chinh xac trong khung hien tai.
  + Goi y bo sung initial function CROT de bieu dien de hon.
- Cau hoi mo:
  + Co thay multi-qubit recursion bang 1-qubit recursion neu bo sung initial functions khac duoc khong?

7.2) Muc 6.2 - Descriptional complexity va first-order theories
- Descriptional complexity dc(f)[n]:
  + So buoc toi thieu de xay ham square_1^QP xap xi/tinh f tren input do dai n.
- Y nghia:
  + Them 1 truc do "suc manh mo ta" khac voi do phuc tap thoi gian.
- Mo rong:
  + Ap dung ca cho ham/ngon ngu khong nam trong BQP/FBQP de do "do gan" voi square_1^QP.
- Huong logic:
  + Mo duong cho first-order quantum theories tren trang thai Hilbert.

7.3) Muc 6.3 - Type-2 quantum functionals
- Type-1:
  + Ham tren chuoi/trang thai thong thuong.
- Type-2:
  + Ham nhan them ham oracle O lam dau vao.
- Xay dung:
  + Dinh nghia tilde(O) tren du lieu da ma hoa.
  + Them initial function QUERY de hoi oracle theo kieu XOR ma hoa.
- Tinh chat:
  + QUERY o QUERY = I (tuong tu involution trong bo canh da cho).
- Y nghia:
  + Mo rong khung ly thuyet sang tinh toan luong tu bac cao.

7.4) Muc 6.4 - Ung dung ngon ngu lap trinh luong tu
- Luong y tuong:
  + Mo ta so do xay ham square_1^QP co the xem nhu "chuong trinh".
  + Moi luoc do = mot loai lenh.
- Gia tri thuc tien:
  + Co the lam nen tang thiet ke DSL/quantum programming language co cau truc ro rang.

